<br />
<p class="text-center"> School may be back in session for many, but summer is still in full bloom!</p>
<br/>


<img src="/images/blogs/whats-blooming-blog/2018-08-31/eupatorium-maculatum-gateway-hms18.jpg" alt="Dakota Sunshine Sunflower" title="Dakota Sunshine Sunflower" class="img-center responsive" style="max-width: 600px;" />
<h5 class="text-center">Dakota Sunshine Sunflower &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<i> Helianthus</i> 'Dakota Sunshine'</h5>
<p class="text-center"> Who doesn't love a couple of sunflowers! They are sure to put a smile on your face.</p>
<br />


<img src="/images/blogs/whats-blooming-blog/2018-08-31/kniphofia-christmas-cheer-hms18.jpg" alt="Blue Blazes Hyssop" title="Blue Blazes Hyssop" class="img-center responsive" style="max-width: 600px;" />
<h5 class="text-center">Blue Blazes Hyssop &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<i> Agastache</i> 'Blue Blazes'</h5>
<p class="text-center"> Check out the long legs on this bee!</p>
<br />


<img src="/images/blogs/whats-blooming-blog/2018-08-31/hibiscus-disco-bell-mix-hms18.jpg" alt="Mongolian Bells™ Clematis" title="Mongolian Bells™ Clematis" class="img-center responsive" style="max-width: 600px;" />
<h5 class="text-center">Mongolian Bells™ Clematis &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<i> Clematis integrifolia</i> 'PSHarlan'</h5>
<p class="text-center"> This long bloomer will tolerate many soil types.</p>
<br />


<img src="/images/blogs/whats-blooming-blog/2018-08-31/eucomis-sparkling-burgundy-hms18.jpg" alt="Pineapple Lily" title="Pineapple Lily" class="img-center responsive" style="max-width: 600px;" />
<h5 class="text-center">Pineapple Lily &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<i> Eucomis</i> 'Sparkling Burgundy'</h5>
<p class="text-center"> This cactus is sporting some large fruit! </p>
<br />


<img src="/images/blogs/whats-blooming-blog/2018-08-31/rosa-playboy-hms18.jpg" alt="Playboy Rose" title="Playboy Rose" class="img-center responsive" style="max-width: 600px;" />
<h5 class="text-center">Playboy Rose &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<i> Rosa</i> 'Playboy'</h5>
<p class="text-center"> These are hop cones! Don't they look cute all snuggled together?! </p>
<br />
<p class="text-center"> All the plants pictured above can be seen in the Water Conservation Garden.</p>
<br />

<p class="text-center"> Whether you are in school, just about to start, or need some stress relief, come relax and surround yourself with nature's beauty up here at Red Butte Garden.</p>
